STATE
v.
Sabas IBARRA. No. 227P08-4. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Nov. 5, 2015. Sabas Ibarra, Burgaw, for Ibarra, Sabas. Kimberly N. Callahan, Assistant Attorney General, for State of NC. Garry W. Frank, District Attorney, for State of NC.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 27th of August 2015 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of November 2015."
